Puggi: An autograph!? Well of course!!

Chiyuki Fan: Thank you so much! I... I always thought I was just an ordinary person, no talent at all. But after seeing your performance...
Chiyuki Fan: I realized, even if I'm ugly and talentless, as long as I give it my all, I can do anything! I can be the belle of the ball!!

Chiyuki: ......
Chiyuki: ......

Puggi: Puggi Puggi~ Seems like everyone wants to be my friend~
Chiyuki: ......
Chiyuki: ...Eh?

Wolf Chieftain: Oh? If it isn't the beautiful Miss Chiyuki...
Chiyuki: Hello, gentlemen. How are you?
Turtle Chieftain: Glad you asked!
Turtle Chieftain: We were fixin' to have a drink or two. Come on, join us!
Wolf Chieftain: Good wine and good company, what do you say?
Chiyuki: ...Well, I still have some things to do, so... maybe now isn't a great time...
Turtle Chieftain: Nonsense! The tournament's 'bout to start. What else have you got to do!?
Turtle Chieftain: That tournament's such a bore... just a bunch'a fightin' and killin'! Come share a drink with us, put us outta our misery!
Wolf Chieftain: Aren't you always saying you want to make everyone happy, Miss Chiyuki? Isn't that your mission?
Wolf Chieftain: Come on, put a smile on our faces~
Chiyuki: (They're tribe chieftains, I have to be polite...)
Chiyuki: I'm very sorry, but I really have to get back...
Wolf Chieftain: Well, well... If I didn't know any better I'd say you were disrespecting us! And you know how important respect is here in the east.
Chiyuki: No, I'm sorry, it's just that I really must get back to the stage...
Chiyuki: (Where is everyone? Please oh please can someone just walk by!? Anyone!?)
Turtle Chieftain: Just quit that smelly ol' stage why don'cha!? We know some people in high places, I bet we could get you some work somewhere else...
Chiyuki: (What the heck are you talking about!? I've worked my butt off to get on that stage, I don't need you two messing it up!)
Chiyuki: I can't go with you. Please, let me—
???: —You two disgust me.

Wolf Chieftain: Hmph, just looks like some poor vagrant...
Wolf Chieftain: Listen, punk, I'll give you one chance to scram. Usually I'd beat you silly, but I'm in a good mood today.
???: Is that right... well unfortunately for you...
???: —I'm in a bad mood.
Chiyuki: (Who is this guy? He's amazing...)
Turtle Chieftain: Guh... What in the...
???: So, still wanna fight? I'm sure these past few days have been tiring.
Wolf Chieftain: S-S-Somebody help!! Help!!!
???: Help who? You? ...As if you're worth it...
Chiyuki: Stop! You'll kill them!
???: Is that such a bad thing?
Chiyuki: I said stop! They've learned their lesson... And if you really kill them, what makes you think the Alliance would let you get away with it?
???: Let them try and arrest me. See if I care.
???: ...Listen here, you filth. This girl has nothing to do with you, and if I see you bothering her again, I swear it will be the end of you.
???: Now get out of here!
???: And you! You want to laugh? Fine. You want to cry? Fine. But pick one, damnit!
Chiyuki: (Cry? Did I... cry in front of him?)
Chiyuki: Sir, if you'd please let me...
Chiyuki: (Eh?)
Chiyuki: (...Where'd he go? I didn't get a chance to thank him...)
